02:52:19.637 --> 02:52:23.210
Things like bridging between synchronous and asynchronous I.O.

02:52:23.955 --> 02:52:26.371
Things like copying things in and out of bytes.

02:52:27.572 --> 02:52:28.411
Things like having...

02:52:32.724 --> 02:52:34.031
